title: The Judicature (Supreme Court) Additional Powers of Registrar Act
title_en: The Judicature (Supreme Court) Additional Powers of Registrar Act
short_name: Judicature (Supreme Court) Additional Powers of Registrar Act

provisions.title: Section 1
provisions.content:
1. This Order may be cited as the Additional Powers of Registrar
Order, 1960.
  2 The Registrar is hereby empowered to exercise jurisdiction in re-
lation to all of the matters specified in the Schedule to the Act, save and
except those contained in sub-paragraph (0) of paragraph ( 1 ) of the
Schedule.
